title: Stitch! Best Friends Forever (Season 3) [C-W]
description:
Stitch  Best Friends Forever (Season 3) [C-W]


Disney Stitch! is an adapted version of the US animated feature film Lilo & Stitch and the subsequent spin-off series. It takes place in the future after the film and started in Japan in October 2008. The show features a Japanese girl named Yuna in place of Lilo, and is set on a fictional island in the Ryukyus off the shore of Okinawa instead of Hawaii

This is the dub as aired on Disney Channel Australia.
